es. Moreover this cluster may have\nexperimented 1 or 2 Gyrs ago a merging with an infalling galaxy group, as\nindicated also by the previous dynamical analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2004 08:55:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
